<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-12097] Combination of path param and query param does not work</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-12097</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If in route are used both path parameter and query parameter:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
restlet:{{data.access.url}}/v2/users/{userId}?projection=full
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;then because of commit :&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/commit/4da8d0ad4472e69a5728f67fa121b3b4150fdc33#diff-470ee30498bbf9ea5b6ea223650c0e1c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/camel/commit/4da8d0ad4472e69a5728f67fa121b3b4150fdc33#diff-470ee30498bbf9ea5b6ea223650c0e1c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;on lines 216-219 are escaped &quot;&lt;/p&gt;
{&quot; &quot;}
&lt;p&gt;&quot; so userId in my example is never replaced.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Escaping is done in URISupport.appendParametersToURI on line:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
URI uri = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; URI(normalizeUri(originalURI));
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;There is workaround to use Exchange.HTTP_QUERY header for query parameter and path must not contain query parameters.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
